Package: cngpld
Type: Package
Title: Case-control Copy-number Analysis Using Gaussian Process Latent Difference
Version: 0.1
Date: 2020-04-10
Author: David J. H. Shih
Maintainer: David J. H. Shih <djh.shih@gmail.com>
Description: Performs comparative copy-number analyses in order to identify
	regions that are more recurrently amplified (or deleted) in 
	cases vs. controls, using a Gaussian process latent difference model to
	control for the covariance structure of genomic data.
Imports: parallel, gpldiff, GenomicRanges
URL: https://bitbucket.org/djhshih/cngpld
BugReports: https://bitbucket.org/djhshih/cngpld/issues
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
